title: MS Office 2007 Enterprise + Visio/Project/SharePoint August 2016
description:
Microsoft Office 2007 Enterprise with Visio Project SharePoint August 2016

About this release

- OS: Windows all, 32-bit/64-bit
- Version: 12.0.6754.5000 SP3 MSO
- Channel: Enterprise
- Updated: August 09, 2016
- Architecture: 32-bit (do not ask for 64-bit version, there is none)
- Language: English (United States)
- Proofing tools: English, French, Spanish
- Activation: valid keys were added to the setup files

Includes

Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, Publisher, Access, InfoPath, Communicator, Groove, OneNote)
Microsoft Office Visio 2007 Professional SP3
Microsoft Office Project 2007 Professional SP3
Microsoft Office SharePoint Designer 2007 SP3

Bonus folder

Required components
Office File Validation
Visual Studio for Office Runtime

Optional
Classic Menu for Office 2007
File Format Converters, PowerPoint Viewer, SaveAs PDF and XPS, Wordviewer

Installation

- Mount / burn / extract
- Install Office / Visio / Project / SharePoint Designer (no key required, valid keys were added to the setup files - keys in text file just in case)
- Install Office File Validation + Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required) from Bonus folder
- Customize your installation with included Add-ins (Bonus folder): Classic Menu for Office 2007 v7.50, FileFormatConverters, PowerPointViewer, SaveAsPDFandXPS, Wordview
